title: Patch 6.10 is live!

embed.description: Greetings, summoners. Welcome to patch 6.10, the oneafter Midseason. We're back to business as usual in terms of our layout this time. 6.9's template is one we break out for special occasions, and 'changing almost everything in League' seemed to fit that description.

body:
Patch 6.10 is now live in OCE. If you discover any issues or bugs after patching please post them here and we'll investigate.

Have a great day & see you on the rift!

Mindstar
